<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_208_r4l1"><expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Eglolfſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> <expan>Lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü Awrbach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_208_r4l2">Lieber her <expan>Lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> / Vns hat fürgelegt <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> von Eppıngen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l3"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvie Jr Jm / in <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> hawſe cʒüm Altprehſthof / <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l5">xvij ſchock ſtürcʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_208_r4l4">die ſein ſeyn / </ab></add> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd er wiſʒ doch nicht / daʒ er mıt ew cʒeſchıcken hab </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l6">
<del rend="strikethrough">dann güt </del> / . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>Eppinge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſ </del> <expan>dıſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l7">habe wider <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvöllet / . vnd getrawen ew vvol Jr laſſet Jn vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l8">genieſʒen / vvan er vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ıſt / . Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> . etc . 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / . </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l9">wan er ſprichet / daʒ er nichts wiſʒ / daʒ Jr mit Jm <expan>cʒeſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l10">Het Jr aber cʒü Jm iht cʒüſprechen / Darvmb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l11"><expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt eins <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l12">rechten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen / wenn vvir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l13"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / anheim ıſt / . vnd laſſet vns des <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r4l14"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>VValp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>is</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="102v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglolfst<ex>ein</ex></expan>, <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> czü
                        Awrbach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>, uns hat
                                                fürgelegt <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                                                Eppingen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie ir im in
                                                  <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> hawse czüm
                                                Altprehsthof <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt
                                                xvii schock stürcz, <add>die sein seyn</add>.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>Eppinge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein habe wider
                                                  <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet; und getrawen
                                                ew wol, ir lasset in unser genieszen, wan er unser
                                                  <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ist. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., wan er
                                                sprichet, daz er nichts wisz, daz ir mit im
                                                  <expan>czeschicke<ex>n</ex></expan> habt; het ir
                                                aber czü im iht czüsprechen, darumb
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                                                  <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt eins
                                                  <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> rechten
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen, wenn wir
                                                des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so
                                                derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist. Und
                                                lasset uns des <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi
                                                  <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
